A Nigerian woman identified as Juliet Njideka Esther and her child have asked Nigerians to join them in praising God after narrowly escaping death. According to the woman, a huge block crashed down from her bedroom ceiling and fell on them while they were sleeping. Sharing her testimony on Tuesday February 18, Mrs Juliet said that the incident happened around 2:30am. “Praise the Lord with us, the devil struck while we were asleep but God gave us victory. This is block that fell on us from the roof around 2:30am today” More photos below.. Source